revideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31974754&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17552088376869a2da847480_53298442"/><published>2025-07-06T01:24:36+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f94a4f2804e296ec754367651fb91a0a</id><title>Hi bor 跌到零都冇用，九龍灣泰峰有五伙撻訂</title><updated>2025-07-06T01:56:48+08:00</updated><author><name>hkduck123</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-06T01:56:48+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573120274"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573120274"&gt;可能系自編自導自演。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31974760&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17552088376869a2da847480_53298442"/><published>2025-07-06T01:56:48+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5a49dc344b4d37a8ca2ccdb2b257dd89</id><title>北京蘭州北京11天, 好長氣的遊記</title><updated>2025-07-03T09:18:46+08:00</updated><author><name>kc60wong</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-03T09:18:46+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573084505"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573084505"&gt;第1天,6月11星期三&lt;br&gt;6月11出發,2人行,乘11.20西九高鐵,一等坐,人仔1997/人, 19.30到北京西站。&lt;br/&gt;近年好少出門,一年只上過幾次深圳。第一次坐高鐵,很興奮。&lt;br/&gt;當日早上10.00去站內添好運食D野,亦已在車上點了外賣。&lt;br/&gt;10.30食完,站內行下睇下, 11.00入閘安檢過關,11.10上車。&lt;br/&gt;原來車門會在開車前5min關閉。準時開車。&lt;br/&gt;個踏腳板安裝在前面坐位,於是後面位仁姐細細力伸一下腳,你就小震一下。&lt;br/&gt;在深圳北送上了KFC葡撻,廣州南送上了水蛋排骨飯, D野都OK好食。&lt;br/&gt;車上服務員送上免費飲品,小吃,似坐飛機。&lt;br/&gt;車上用alipay買了杯咖啡,poor。可能訊號弱,想網上定野比錢,好多失敗&lt;br/&gt;想定故宮門票,原來要好多日預定,最後在trip.com&lt;br/&gt;定了6月19,有領隊,有填鴨餐的票,約250/人。&lt;br/&gt;又定了13日恭王府門票, 20元/人。&lt;br/&gt;7.30準時到北京西。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31972442&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1076&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-07-03T09:18:46+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>375893a4e3ce58e60012de67fe7e5a6e</id><title>到此一遊系列 - 馬巒山防詐騙玩水R荔枝一日遊</title><updated>2025-06-30T14:50:33+08:00</updated><author><name>kingkong_hk</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-30T14:50:33+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573050416"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573050416"&gt;趁呢幾日落過雨要安排玩水路線, 馬巒山郊野公園位於龍崗區坪山, 要預較多交通時間&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;由蓮塘口岸打車來碧嶺入口(西北門)大約45分鐘, 高鐵西九龍去高鐵坪山站55分鐘仲可以順手玩埋雲巴, 再轉駁公車過來大約30分鐘&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_111849.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_111849.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/5ccc0b/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_111849.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;唔熟地形睇呢個地圖都幾R頭, 今次係來玩碧嶺瀑布群步道&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112756.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112756.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/bd6289/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112756.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;反詐騙主題公園乜都冇算唔算詐騙&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112927.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112927.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/539b20/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112927.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;目測山體唔超過500米高, 但又有深圳最大瀑布群玩&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112959.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112959.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/06cb05/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_112959.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;睇來都幾多遊人來玩&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113419.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113419.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/6e84d7/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113419.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;M480公車由高鐵坪山站來呢度&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113602.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113602.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/390d1a/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113602.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;指示牌都好充足&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113639.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113639.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/1c71ce/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_113639.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;見到對岸農莊有荔枝樹過去R左幾粒食幾好味&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114125.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114125.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/7fb59b/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114125.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;4蚊人仔買咗半斤一路行一路食住先&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114352.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114352.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/4a2bee/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114352.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;見好多人玩緊水&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114205.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114205.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/eea6bf/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114205.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;郊野公園竟然有KFC&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114718.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114718.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/32973e/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_114718.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;步道都係人工靚路搞得好企理&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115229.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115229.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/762d05/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115229.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;咁多人影相一定有好嘢&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115421.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115421.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/aba0ae/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115421.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;銀河瀑&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115607.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115607.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/93e18c/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_115607.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;繼續上探&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120130.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120130.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/2a8bca/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120130.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;呢個唔知叫咩名&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120327.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120327.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/adc8e6/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120327.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;再上探&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120922.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120922.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d2f390/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_120922.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;跟路牌去九天瀑&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_121209.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_121209.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/960a88/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_121209.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;潭水比較靜位置會開放可以落去玩&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124151.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124151.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/0697c9/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124151.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;九天瀑&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124806.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124806.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/520c0f/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_124806.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;行咗入深谷, 好處係太陽曬唔到咁多入來&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125409.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125409.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/57ef4d/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125409.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;298米位原路折反, 門外就走出咗郊野公園範圍, 出去向前行就係東部華橋城, 大約2-3KM路程可到茶溪谷&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125903.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125903.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a14773/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_125903.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;飛龍瀑, 呢度水急有圍封但好多人照行出去影相&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131020.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131020.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/efde8f/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131020.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;要去打邊爐所以落山會比較趕時間&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131323.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131323.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a5b3c9/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_131323.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;影毛蟲都玩咗成個字&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_123305.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_123305.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/8bf5ef/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_123305.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_132420.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_132420.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d11c2a/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_132420.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;水潭位可以沖下對鞋&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_133300.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_133300.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/251d81/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_133300.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;隊友食完話要返轉頭買荔枝&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140958.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140958.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/38739f/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140958.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;即時剪落來賣8蚊斤抵到爛&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140647.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140647.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/b107f3/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140647.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;睇來今年荔枝多到賣唔晒&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140840.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140840.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/6c7d90/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/IMG_20250629_140840.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;路線圖: 馬巒山郊野公園西北門 =&amp;gt; 飛龍瀑, 原路反回, 約6KM&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573050416" original-img="http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/map.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/map.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/c6a023/f/800x0/http://album.king-kong.org/china/MaluanHill/map.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31970156&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1076&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-06-30T14:50:33+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>015c5e7d28d448ddca33d4009eecf2c9</id><title>高明錦鯉文化園</title><updated>2025-07-01T16:28:24+08:00</updated><author><name>timmywu</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-01T16:28:24+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573063156"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573063156"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16338641" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="posit